02:45.898 --> 02:47.640
[Marcus]: Look, I'm sorry,
I shouldn't have said anything.

02:47.740 --> 02:50.443
I just, I needed
to know the truth.

02:50.543 --> 02:52.886
You're not after the truth.

02:52.986 --> 02:55.368
Nah, you just...

02:55.468 --> 02:56.729
wanna prove
your hero's innocent,

02:56.829 --> 02:59.853
no matter who gets destroyed
in the process, huh?

02:59.953 --> 03:01.735
You want us to declare
Quebert a saint

03:01.835 --> 03:04.577
because maybe he didn't kill
the 15-year-old girl

03:04.677 --> 03:05.899
he was having an affair with?

03:05.999 --> 03:08.862
He was not having
an affair with her.

03:08.962 --> 03:10.784
You sure picked a hell of a guy
for a best friend.

03:10.884 --> 03:13.607
Only friend, actually.

03:19.773 --> 03:21.435
[Marcus]:
Tisha, thank you so much.

03:21.535 --> 03:23.797
The meal was, uh...
it was fantastic.

03:23.897 --> 03:25.839
[Tisha]: Well, I'm glad
you could join us, Marcus.

03:25.939 --> 03:26.760
[Marcus]: Me too.

03:26.860 --> 03:28.722
Why can't I read it?

03:28.822 --> 03:30.844
Maybe when
you're older.

03:30.944 --> 03:32.045
It's not really
meant for, um...

03:32.145 --> 03:33.847
Anyone.

03:33.947 --> 03:34.848
Don't listen to him.

03:34.948 --> 03:36.049
It's wonderful.

03:36.149 --> 03:37.771
Thank you.

03:37.871 --> 03:39.533
All right, girls.

03:39.633 --> 03:41.575
Let's do
the homework, okay?

03:41.675 --> 03:43.677
Let's do it,
both of you.

03:48.802 --> 03:50.744
So, I've been going through
that police report

03:50.844 --> 03:51.785
on Nola's
disappearance.

03:51.885 --> 03:52.666
Yeah.

03:52.766 --> 03:53.787
The one written
by Chief Pratt.

03:53.887 --> 03:55.709
No mention
of Stern or Harry.

03:55.809 --> 03:57.912
Really?

03:58.012 --> 03:59.073
Well, because
Nancy said

03:59.173 --> 04:00.754
that she told
Pratt about Stern

04:00.854 --> 04:01.796
after Nola
disappeared.

04:01.896 --> 04:02.877
Mm-hm.

04:02.977 --> 04:03.717
And then
Tamara Quinn

04:03.817 --> 04:04.839
said that
she showed him

04:04.939 --> 04:06.440
that incriminating paper

04:06.540 --> 04:08.963
she took from
Harry's house, so...

04:09.063 --> 04:09.804
And the report's signed

04:09.904 --> 04:11.906
by Pratt himself.

04:12.867 --> 04:14.849
With all
due respect, sir,

04:14.949 --> 04:17.892
Mrs. Quinn showed you
what Harry wrote about her.

04:17.992 --> 04:19.133
Nancy Hattaway told you

04:19.233 --> 04:20.855
about her relationship
with Stern,

04:20.955 --> 04:22.096
and yet nothing

04:22.196 --> 04:24.198
is mentioned in the case file.

04:24.839 --> 04:27.862
I combed the area for weeks

04:27.962 --> 04:30.465
looking for that girl,

04:30.565 --> 04:33.908
using every available resource,

04:34.008 --> 04:38.473
and you question my work?

04:38.573 --> 04:40.915
Cops don't do that
to other cops!

04:41.015 --> 04:43.137
The good ones do.

05:09.885 --> 05:11.226
All I ever wanted to be

05:11.326 --> 05:14.649
was a good cop...

05:15.891 --> 05:18.754
but sometimes...

05:18.854 --> 05:22.237
circumstances
beyond your control,

05:22.337 --> 05:24.840
they make you...

05:24.940 --> 05:27.803
do things.

05:27.903 --> 05:31.126
You keep it inside you
long enough,

05:31.226 --> 05:34.169
you get cancer.

05:34.269 --> 05:36.271
[knocking]

05:39.955 --> 05:44.700
She still thinks
I'm in remission.

05:44.800 --> 05:46.622
Why didn't you carry out
the investigation

05:46.722 --> 05:49.765
like you should've?

05:53.088 --> 05:55.911
What are you
hiding, Chief?

05:56.011 --> 05:58.013
Hmm?

06:03.099 --> 06:03.879
You can tell me here,

06:03.979 --> 06:05.962
or we can, uh...

06:06.062 --> 06:07.163
I can get a subpoena

06:07.263 --> 06:09.986
and force you to talk.

06:12.188 --> 06:14.811
No need.

06:14.911 --> 06:16.813
It's time.

06:16.913 --> 06:18.935
[sighing]

06:19.035 --> 06:23.319
I don't want to die
with this on my conscience.

06:29.085 --> 06:31.868
It was, uh...

06:31.968 --> 06:36.993
it was early August
when she came to see me.

06:37.093 --> 06:38.114
<i>[knock on door]</i>

06:38.214 --> 06:40.997
Mm-hm? Come in!

06:41.097 --> 06:42.759
Oh.

06:42.859 --> 06:45.682
Well, hello, Nola.

06:45.782 --> 06:47.784
What's going on?

06:51.107 --> 06:52.008
Can I, uh...

06:52.108 --> 06:54.310
can I help you with something?

06:56.873 --> 06:58.875
Nola, do you--

06:59.316 --> 07:01.017
No, that's insane.
There's no way--

07:01.117 --> 07:02.739
It's the truth.

07:02.839 --> 07:03.900
I swear.

07:04.000 --> 07:06.343
That girl...

07:06.443 --> 07:09.846
knew exactly what she was doing.

07:11.448 --> 07:15.132
Now you're a criminal.

07:20.777 --> 07:23.340
You're the goddamn
chief of police.

07:26.103 --> 07:27.364
You couldn't resist the advances

07:27.464 --> 07:29.366
of a 15-year-old-girl?

07:29.466 --> 07:30.968
And...

07:31.068 --> 07:35.873
I take full
responsibility for that.

07:38.355 --> 07:41.659
And what happened the...

07:41.759 --> 07:44.361
the following week...

07:51.889 --> 07:52.830
Oh, my God.

07:52.930 --> 07:54.111
Oh, my-- Chief!

07:54.211 --> 07:55.993
Chief, what did you do?

07:56.093 --> 07:56.994
Where are you take...

07:57.094 --> 07:58.155
Where are they
taking my husband?

07:58.255 --> 08:00.117
Detec...

08:00.217 --> 08:02.840
Chief! Chief!

08:02.940 --> 08:05.403
Listen to me, ma'am, please.

08:05.503 --> 08:07.084
[Maggie screaming]
Chief, what did you do?

08:07.184 --> 08:08.366
Calm down right now.

08:08.466 --> 08:09.327
Watch your head.

08:09.427 --> 08:11.369
Chief...

08:11.469 --> 08:13.051
You need to take it
easy here, okay?

08:13.151 --> 08:15.253
Where are you
taking him?

08:15.353 --> 08:16.414
Chief!

08:16.514 --> 08:18.936
[siren wails]

08:19.036 --> 08:22.140
[Maggie screams]

08:22.240 --> 08:23.781
<i>Gareth Pratt,</i>

08:23.881 --> 08:25.063
<i>Sommerdale's former</i>
<i>chief of police,</i>

08:25.163 --> 08:28.066
<i>has admitted to engaging</i>
<i>in sexual acts</i>

08:28.166 --> 08:30.108
<i>with 15-year-old</i>
<i>Nola Kellergan,</i>

08:30.208 --> 08:32.350
<i>and is now a suspect</i>
<i>in her murder.</i>

08:32.450 --> 08:34.993
<i>In other news</i>
<i>at city hall today...</i>

08:35.093 --> 08:36.715
You okay, sweetie?

08:36.815 --> 08:38.076
I-I trusted him
with my life.

08:38.176 --> 08:41.299
Now it's like
I hardly knew the guy.

08:42.981 --> 08:44.983
Pratt has been arrested.

08:47.185 --> 08:48.146
Harry, why would Pratt
lie about this?

08:48.226 --> 08:49.728
Shut up, Marcus!

08:49.828 --> 08:51.449
I refuse to believe
this garbage!

08:51.549 --> 08:53.171
You remember when I asked you
about Elijah Stern?

08:53.271 --> 08:54.072
I think you should
leave now.

08:54.152 --> 08:55.333
Nola...

08:55.433 --> 08:56.735
Nola had a relationship
with him

08:56.835 --> 08:58.457
that same
summer, okay?

08:58.557 --> 09:00.058
[slams table]

09:00.158 --> 09:01.059
Why are you doing this?

09:01.159 --> 09:03.181
-I'm sorr--
-Why?

09:03.281 --> 09:04.863
Why are you trying
to destroy everything?

09:04.963 --> 09:05.464
Shit... no!

09:05.564 --> 09:07.566
[raging]

