I'm here!

10:00.059 --> 10:01.240
I love it!

10:01.340 --> 10:03.342
Ah!

10:06.265 --> 10:07.367
Is this what
you're looking for?

10:07.467 --> 10:09.469
Oh, God, yes.

10:11.350 --> 10:13.252
I'm sorry, you were sleeping,
and I took it home to read.

10:13.352 --> 10:14.254
Oh, my God...

10:14.354 --> 10:16.055
