10:51.992 --> 10:53.013
Don't forget to eat.

10:53.113 --> 10:56.176
Otherwise, you'll get
one of your migraines.

10:56.276 --> 10:58.278
Thank you.

11:02.723 --> 11:04.625
Where are you going?

11:04.725 --> 11:08.028
Busy. [giggles]

11:08.128 --> 11:09.510
Women must remain mysterious.

11:09.610 --> 11:12.312
I read that in a magazine.

11:12.412 --> 11:14.234
See you tomorrow?

11:14.334 --> 11:15.476
Yes.

11:15.576 --> 11:17.358
Thank you.

11:17.458 --> 11:19.460
You're welcome.

12:28.690 --> 12:30.392
Please get undressed.

12:30.492 --> 12:33.014
I'll go tell Mr. Stern
you have arrived.

12:42.424 --> 12:46.128
[rain pouring]

12:46.228 --> 12:48.510
[clock tower bells chime]

13:02.764 --> 13:04.626
Harry?

13:04.726 --> 13:06.028
Hey.

13:06.128 --> 13:07.429
Oh! Oh...

13:07.529 --> 13:08.230
Oh, whoa, whoa, whoa!

13:08.330 --> 13:09.151
There you go.

13:09.251 --> 13:10.392
Oh, thank you.
[chuckles]

13:10.492 --> 13:11.473
So it's true!

13:11.573 --> 13:12.414
You really do
come out this early

13:12.494 --> 13:13.355
to go running?

13:13.455 --> 13:15.277
Yeah, I try never
to miss a sunrise.

13:15.377 --> 13:16.518
Um...

13:16.618 --> 13:17.680
It looks like you found

13:17.780 --> 13:20.362
a new way to
commute to work.

13:20.462 --> 13:21.443
Yeah, I'm just
learning, actually.

13:21.543 --> 13:22.404
Uh-huh?

13:22.504 --> 13:24.086
Mm-hm.
Um...

13:24.186 --> 13:25.608
I haven't seen you
much lately.

13:25.708 --> 13:26.609
Yeah, I know.

13:26.709 --> 13:28.370
I'm sorry, it's just, you know,

13:28.470 --> 13:30.473
I've been so busy
with the book and everything.

13:31.193 --> 13:32.455
I hope you're not mad at me

13:32.555 --> 13:33.315
for going to
the Summer Gala with Travis.

13:33.395 --> 13:34.497
No, no, no, no, no.

13:34.597 --> 13:35.778
Don't be silly. No.

13:35.878 --> 13:37.380
I don't love him,
you know.

13:37.480 --> 13:38.461
He's just a friend.

13:38.561 --> 13:39.382
Jenny...

13:39.482 --> 13:41.764
I love someone else.

13:44.447 --> 13:47.250
It's true. So...

13:53.496 --> 13:54.437
A little blush for you.

13:54.537 --> 13:56.439
Oh. Yeah.

13:56.539 --> 13:58.081
I... I gotta...

13:58.181 --> 13:59.322
Bye, Harry.

13:59.422 --> 14:01.424
I'll see you.

14:02.425 --> 14:04.427
Ooh...

14:10.513 --> 14:11.574
[Jenny screams]

14:11.674 --> 14:13.456
Oh! Oh, my...
Luther, you scared me! Geez!

14:13.556 --> 14:14.497
What does he want
from you?

14:14.597 --> 14:15.458
Ow! Nothing!

14:15.558 --> 14:16.379
What does he want
from you?

14:16.479 --> 14:17.380
Ow! He's a friend.

14:17.480 --> 14:18.341
You're hurting me!

14:18.441 --> 14:19.542
Geez! Ow!

14:19.642 --> 14:20.704
Have you thought
about my proposal?

14:20.804 --> 14:22.706
The answer is no!
Now, let go of me!

14:22.806 --> 14:23.667
Let go of me!

14:23.767 --> 14:26.169
Help! Help! Help!

14:29.933 --> 14:31.675
[car door opens
and closes]

14:31.775 --> 14:33.196
[engine starting]

14:33.296 --> 14:34.798
Ow...

14:34.898 --> 14:36.900
[car drives away]

15:06.330 --> 15:07.311
Hey.

15:07.411 --> 15:08.352
You need some help?

15:08.452 --> 15:09.433
Yeah.

15:09.533 --> 15:11.235
I think I overdid it.

15:11.335 --> 15:12.877
Here, you can get in.

15:12.977 --> 15:14.198
I'll take you home.

15:14.298 --> 15:16.160
Thanks.
Yeah, I think I...

15:16.260 --> 15:18.482
[wincing] Geez!

15:18.582 --> 15:19.323
I don't know,
I think I...

15:19.423 --> 15:22.266
I think I pulled
something.

15:24.949 --> 15:26.691
You're in Sommerdale

15:26.791 --> 15:28.532
awfully early
this morning.

15:28.632 --> 15:30.815
Mornings are my
favorite time of day.

15:30.915 --> 15:33.177
Mine too.

15:33.277 --> 15:35.279
It's usually when I get
my best writing done.

15:47.492 --> 15:48.553
Luther, thanks
for the ride.

15:48.653 --> 15:49.674
I appreciate it.

15:49.774 --> 15:51.776
I'm not sure I would've
made it without you.

