<i>changed her life forever.</i>

38:08.372 --> 38:10.074
<i>We went over our plan,</i>

38:10.174 --> 38:11.596
<i>that I'd be leaving</i>
<i>the next morning,</i>

38:11.696 --> 38:14.759
