<i>so that people would see me,</i>

38:14.859 --> 38:16.841
<i>and I could tell them that</i>
<i>I'd be away for a week or two</i>

38:16.941 --> 38:18.963
<i>for business in Boston.</i>

38:19.063 --> 38:21.205
<i>Then, on August 30th,</i>

38:21.305 --> 38:24.008
<i>I would wait for her</i>
<i>at the By the Sea Motel,</i>

38:24.108 --> 38:27.172
<i>Room 8, at 8:00 p.m.</i>

38:27.272 --> 38:29.974
<i>We'd cross the border</i>
<i>into Canada,</i>

38:30.074 --> 38:31.976
<i>find a small apartment to rent,</i>

38:32.076 --> 38:34.018
<i>then I'd return to Goose Cove</i>
<i>a few days later,</i>

38:34.118 --> 38:38.063
<i>give the keys back,</i>
<i>and leave Sommerdale for good,</i>

38:38.163 --> 38:39.464
<i>explaining that</i>
<i>my novel was finished,</i>

38:39.564 --> 38:41.106
<i>and I'd have to go</i>
<i>back to New York</i>

38:41.206 --> 38:45.830
<i>to deal with its publication.</i>

38:45.930 --> 38:46.971
She was looking forward
to getting married

38:47.052 --> 38:49.254
when she turned 18...

38:50.535 --> 38:52.878
Publish the book.

38:52.978 --> 38:54.840
I would become a professor.

38:54.940 --> 38:58.804
We'd get a dog.

38:58.904 --> 39:02.768
I'd never been so happy
in my entire life...

39:02.868 --> 39:06.071
